OL,3,CTeenager arrested after vehicle driven
OL,4,Ctowards group of women
OL,6,FA teenager has been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of attempted murder, after a
OL,8,Fvehicle was driven towards a group of
OL,9,Fwomen in Northumberland, leaving one
OL,10,Fwith life-threatening injuries.
OL,12,FPolice were called by the ambulance
OL,13,Fservice at around 1.25am on Friday (12
OL,14,FJune), to reports that two people had
OL,15,Fbeen injured on Keelmans Terrace,
OL,16,Fclose to the junction with Beaumont
OL,17,FStreet, in Blyth.
OL,19,FIt was reported that a vehicle had
OL,20,Fbeen driven towards a group of women
OL,21,Fwho were standing on the path.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/3
