PN,39202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1781539876
OL,3,CTeenager arrested after vehicle driven
OL,4,Ctowards group of women
OL,6,FThe vehicle struck two women, both
OL,7,Faged in their 30s, and then left the
OL,8,Fscene.
OL,10,FOne of them suffered serious injuries
OL,11,Fand remains in hospital in a life-
OL,12,Fthreatening condition, meanwhile the
OL,13,Fother woman suffered injuries which
OL,14,Fwere not serious.
OL,16,FLater in the day on Friday, a 17-year-
OL,17,Fold boy was arrested on suspicion of
OL,18,Fattempted murder.
OL,20,FHe has since been released on police
OL,21,Fbail pending further enquiries.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/3
