PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1781539876
OL,3,CTeenager arrested after vehicle driven
OL,4,Ctowards group of women
OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Graeme Barr,
OL,7,Fof Northumbria Police's Major
OL,8,FInvestigation Team (MIT), said: "This
OL,9,Fhas clearly been a very serious
OL,10,Fincident which has resulted in two
OL,11,Fpeople being injured, with one left in
OL,12,Fa life-threatening condition.
OL,14,F"The investigation is at an early
OL,15,Fstage, but we do believe that those
OL,16,Finvolved are known to each other."
OL,18,FNorthumbria Police are urging any
OL,19,Fwitnesses, or anyone with information
OL,20,Fthat could help their investigation,
OL,21,Fto get in touch with them.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/3
